title: Aliexpress DataHub

api_list.name: Custom Endpoint
api_list.description: Custom defined endpoint, more info by contacting support.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://aliexpress-datahub.p.rapidapi.com/custom"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "aliexpress-datahub.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
